      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO JEANIE (5) improved again, beaten a whisker here in a 76 over this distance and gets weight relief off that. Maps for a soft run, and this is her chance. MAGNAPRIME (1) was beaten 2L in the same race, disappointing as the favourite.  Was heavily bet over 1400m prior, beaten a whisker. Deserves another chance. EARENDEL (3) resumed and led that contest, finishing 1.6L away. Will be tougher to peg back with the extra fitness. BENEFICIARY (2) keeps winning and did a good job leading all the way over 1600m last time. Switches back to 1400m but flies over the distance at the track, and from the inside gate is sure to be right in it.",
